<h2>Our Healthcare Consulting Process</h2>
<div class="process-timeline">
<div class="process-step">
<div class="step-number">1</div>
<h3>Practice Assessment</h3>
<p>Comprehensive analysis of your current operations, financials, and clinical workflows to identify improvement opportunities.</p>
<span class="timeline">Week 1-2</span>
</div>
<div class="process-step">
<div class="step-number">2</div>
<h3>Data Analysis</h3>
<p>Deep dive into your revenue cycle, operational metrics, and financial performance to quantify opportunities.</p>
<span class="timeline">Week 2-3</span>
</div>
<div class="process-step">
<div class="step-number">3</div>
<h3>Strategy Development</h3>
<p>Create customized improvement plan with prioritized initiatives, expected ROI, and implementation roadmap.</p>
<span class="timeline">Week 3-4</span>
</div>
<div class="process-step">
<div class="step-number">4</div>
<h3>Implementation Support</h3>
<p>Hands-on assistance implementing changes, training staff, and establishing new processes.</p>
<span class="timeline">Month 2-3</span>
</div>
<div class="process-step">
<div class="step-number">5</div>
<h3>Performance Monitoring</h3>
<p>Track KPIs, measure results, and make adjustments to ensure sustained improvements.</p>
<span class="timeline">Ongoing</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- Case Study Preview -->
<section class="case-study-preview">
<div class="container">
<h2>Healthcare Consulting Success Story</h2>
<div class="case-study-card">
<h3>Multi-Specialty Medical Group - Rhode Island</h3>
<div class="case-details">
<div class="challenge">
<h4>Challenge:</h4>
<p>50-physician group experiencing 25% denial rate, 65-day revenue cycle, and declining profitability despite growing patient volume.</p>
</div>
<div class="solution">
<h4>Our Solution:</h4>
<ul>
<li>Redesigned revenue cycle processes</li>
<li>Implemented denial prevention program</li>
<li>Optimized scheduling and patient flow</li>
<li>Negotiated improved payer contracts</li>
<li>Established KPI dashboards</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="results">
<h4>Results:</h4>
<div class="result-metrics">
<span><strong>$3.2M</strong> Annual Revenue Increase</span>
<span><strong>12%</strong> Denial Rate (from 25%)</span>
<span><strong>42 Days</strong> Revenue Cycle (from 65)</span>
<span><strong>18%</strong> Margin Improvement</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

